{"tid":2171703,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACKPINK 公開新歌預告　Selena Gomez 告白「我一直是妳們的粉絲」！","createTime":"2020-08-24T06:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T15:08:17.000Z","uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2a29218e29b159d284b666049d83a3959399243b","tid":2171703,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T06:37:36.000Z","msg":"BLACKPINK 即將發行新歌 &quot;Ice Cream&quot;，在公開 MV 預告片前，她們先釋出了一小段和 Selena Gomez 互動的特別紀錄！<br />\n<br />\nYG Entertainment 於 23 日晚間公開了 BLACKPINK 新歌 &ldquo;Ice Cream&rdquo; 的首支預告片，搶先揭曉四人和本次合作對象 Selena Gomez 視訊連線時的情況。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dGCSeyKL5dE&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdGCSeyKL5dE%26feature%3Demb_title&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzsgogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=c5c8c9c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dGCSeyKL5dE&amp;feature=emb_title</a><br />\n<br />\nSelena Gomez 跟 BLACKPINK 說：「我真的很興奮，因為我一直以來都是妳們的粉絲，和妳們合作對我來說是個很大的夢想，我真的等不及了！」BLACKPINK 聞言後也非常驚喜。儘管這段影片只有短短 27 秒，也並未揭曉太多新歌的資訊和旋律，依然在公開半天內便吸引逾 100 萬人次觀看。<br />\n<br />\nBLACKPINK 今天已公開 Jisoo 的最新概念照，並將於 28 日下午 1 點（韓國時間）在全球同步發行 &ldquo;Ice Cream&rdquo;，這首歌是否會和 &quot;How You Like That&quot; 一樣迅速橫掃各國排行榜呢？就讓我們拭目以待吧！"},{"pid":"f776bbaa3760e1b297378cae17fb2e78b1d95e5f","tid":2171703,"uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T06:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_b23a842d713bd90a88436246da79463a/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-08-24/129486-868165.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_b23a842d713bd90a88436246da79463a%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-08-24%2F129486-868165.jpg&h=5aef5190&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_f0332a51b76d158665f1ab1e4e64732c/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-08-24/129486-868150.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u